Layout Guidelines
Grid System

12-column grid with 24px gutters. Responsive breakpoints at 640px, 768px, 1024px, and 1280px.

Containers

Max-width containers: 1280px for main content, 768px for focused content areas.

White Space

Maintain generous white space to enhance readability and create visual hierarchy. Use consistent spacing units from the spacing system.